25
00:00:59,000 --> 00:01:02,000
and gradually add more features as you learn.

26
00:01:02,000 --> 00:01:05,003
It's like furnishing your house one room at a time.

27
00:01:05,003 --> 00:01:09,000
- To sum up, JavaScript adds functionality to our websites.


28
00:01:09,000 --> 00:01:11,001
It's an essential skill for web developers,

29
00:01:11,001 --> 00:01:21,001
